teetime.framework.pipe

Interface IPipe

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractInterThreadPipe, AbstractIntraThreadPipe, AbstractPipe, DummyPipe, InstantiationPipe

    public interface IPipe
    Represents a pipe that connects an output port with an input port.
